#! /bin/sh /usr/share/dpatch/dpatch-run
## 10_disable_cache.dpatch by  <fpeters@debian.org>
##
## All lines beginning with `## DP:' are a description of the patch.
## DP: Do not cache downloaded files in memory to plug a giant memory hole
## DP: (see Debian bug #372166)

@DPATCH@
